name: Tres Cool - Cool Enhancing 'Mint of Intent'

metadata.name: ERC-Cool™ All Area Lift Pass #1
metadata.description: To celebrate the auspicious occasion of ERC-Cool being deployed to the world wide web, we cordially invite you to participate in the cool-enhancing 'Mint of Intent'. Part POAP, part collective proof of concept, the Tres Cool™ 'All Area Lift Pass" is the first collection created upon the open source, carbon removing, sustainable ERC-Cool smart contract. Minting says a lot about you and the way you live your life, signaling to the world your esteemed presence within the internet's coolest and proving that you’re not only excessively cool, but early. Go you.
